<codeline><highlight class="normal">```python</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">async<sp/>def<sp/>health_check(client:<sp/>P2PClient)<sp/>-&gt;<sp/>bool:</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/>&quot;&quot;&quot;健康检查&quot;&quot;&quot;</highlight></codeline>
